SubProfile

public SubProfile(java.lang.String name,
                  java.lang.String description,
                  int bgcolor,
                  int timeLeftColor,
                  int timeSpentColor,
                  int frameColor,
                  int totalTime,
                  boolean changeColor)
Default constructor

Parameters:
name - Name of subprofile
description - description is no longer used, but autogenerated in WOMBAT
bgcolor - the background color of the timer
timeLeftColor - The color which represent the time left
timeSpentColor - The color which represent the time consumed
frameColor - The color of the timer frame
totalTime - The time which the timer should count down from
changeColor - true = on, false = off. Used to add a gradient effect between timeLeftColor and timeSpentColor.
